    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and still has that fresh new-car smell! You won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like a dream and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come see it for yourself and take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
