      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3, representing the pinnacle of the S54 naturally aspirated straight-six. This specimen features a meticulously maintained valvetrain with a documented VANOS overhaul and recent valve clearance adjustment. The chassis is structurally flawless, having received proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure torsional rigidity under high-load cornering. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing unparalleled mechanical feedback. The factory suspension remains true to original geometry, offering the perfect balance of damping and rebound. The exterior retains its deep luster with no evidence of panel gap variance or paint degradation, while the interior remains a time capsule of Nappa leather and functional ergonomics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service records available. Clean title.",
