    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on fair-weather days. The original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain supple and firm, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, while every button and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records from day one. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 46500.0,
