    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or door ding to be found, and the interior still has that fresh smell. It drives like an absolute dream. I'm really looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let's get you in the driver's seat!",
      "price": 44500.0,
