    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies, delivering exceptional volumetric efficiency. The critical double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural weak point\u2014has been proactively reinforced with plates to ensure chassis rigidity. Power is managed via the Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, providing tactile engagement and precise torque distribution. The suspension maintains factory geometry with fresh bushings and original dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling characteristics remain intact. No deferred maintenance; this is a mechanically flawless, turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
